HS); M Welch (Dunfermline HS), S McKinnon (Queen Victoria School), C Buchanan
(George Watson's College), J White (George Watson's College), T Boyd
(Hutchesons' GS), P Phillips (Gordonstoun), R Muir (Fettes), G Howieson
(Hutchesons' GS).
